            , not in custody), for <rs id="t17960217-70-off415" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17960217-70-off415" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17960217-70-off415" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               forging and counterfeiting, and uttering and publishing the same as true, on the <rs id="t17960217-70-cd416" type="crimeDate">29th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960217-70-off415 t17960217-70-cd416"></join>, a certain paper, purporting to be the last will and testament of 
                     <persName id="t17960217-70-person706">
                        Henry
                         Lewis
                     <interp inst="t17960217-70-person706" type="surname" value="Lewis"></interp>
